Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.95,0:24:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.75,0:24:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有載過人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.98,0:24:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.39,0:24:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.43,0:24:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長起來那麼沒分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.53,0:24:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也該為地球多想想
